    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "This beaded pendant crafted by Lyrune-Quah shamans features an uncut moonstone that warns the wearer of danger. When a hostile creature comes within 30 feet of you, the stone glows with moonlight only you can see.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
